query:
SELECT 
  address,
  priceYen,
  priceYen / 10000 as price_man,
  areaSqm,
  (priceYen / 10000) / areaSqm as price_per_sqm_man,
  buildingAge,
  nearestStation,
  walkingMinutes
FROM transactions
WHERE prefecture = '神奈川県' 
  AND city = '横浜市中区' 
  AND propertyType = 'マンション'
LIMIT 10;
